            <div type="translation">
                <p>Invocation of the servant of the God Christophoros Omotes and his wife Maria</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>According to <bibl><ptr target="#Mouriki1984"/>,<citedRange> 192</citedRange></bibl>, the donors Christophoros Omotes (for the word ὀμώτης see <bibl><ptr target="#Rhoby2021"/>, <citedRange>345-46</citedRange></bibl>) and his wife Maria financed the mural of Saint Christopher and possibly the depictions of Saints Theodore and Paul which are in the same frame as Saint Christopher. The individual donation it seems that was made at the same period with the main decoration of the church.
</p>
